{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"514c06e4ab","title":"叶剑英传达毛主席的指示","origin":"1967年3月北京玻璃总厂红卫兵联络站编《中央首长讲话（1）》","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"de381f801f","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":27,"articleId":"514c06e4ab"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"aa048f8141","name":"夺权","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"bcecfeaa3a","name":"叶剑英","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"},{"id":"eee1eed029","name":"叶剑英"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c8137ec90d","type":"title","text":"叶剑英传达毛主席的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"514c06e4ab"},{"id":"b55acc85c8","type":"authors","text":"叶剑英毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"514c06e4ab"},{"id":"f4a641c092","type":"paragraph","text":"一、我认为十三个军区不要同时搞，要有前有后。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"514c06e4ab"},{"id":"f7d1ae7e9b","type":"paragraph","text":"二、地方文化大革命正在猛烈开展，夺权斗争还在激烈进行，我们军队要支持革命左派进行斗争，因此军队和地方文化大革命要差开。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"514c06e4ab"},{"id":"364b6c9292","type":"paragraph","text":"三、现在国际上帝、修、反正利用我们文化大革命继续大搞反华活动。如苏联在镇压学生，新疆边境飞机活动增多了。地面部队要有所警惕，要有所准备。如济南、南京、福州、广州、昆明等地区。所以文化大革命时间要稍推一下。将来一定要搞的，顾大局。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"514c06e4ab"}],"page":{"id":"c9938cff63","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"514c06e4ab","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}